text: Novoklyuchevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mishkinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 154 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Mishkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Novoklyuchevo
